{"id":1482,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":3,"title":"Conversation 3","subtitle":"Dropping Off Documents","level":"A2","parts":13,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-3.1482/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-3-2024-08-18-22-20-31/0-conversation-3.mp3","transcript":"Hi, I'm Demi Geard.\nIs Mrs. Hayley in?\nI'm one of her clients.\nMrs. Hayley is traveling abroad until the end of next week.\nIs it urgent?\nI can try to reach her at the resort.\nNo need for that.\nI just came by to drop off these documents she asked me to sign.\nCan I leave them with you?\nSure, no problem!\nI'll let her know you dropped them off and give them to her when she returns.\nHere's a post-it, can you write down what it's about so she knows?\nSure, I'll do that.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:59:33","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hi, I'm Demi Geard.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-3-2024-08-18-22-20-31/1.mp3","time_start":0.0,"time_end":1.79},{"position":2,"content":"Is Mrs. Hayley in?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-3-2024-08-18-22-20-31/2.mp3","time_start":1.79,"time_end":3.26},{"position":3,"content":"I'm one of her clients.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-3-2024-08-18-22-20-31/3.mp3","time_start":3.26,"time_end":4.85},{"position":4,"content":"Mrs. Hayley is traveling abroad until the end of next week.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-3-2024-08-18-22-20-31/4.mp3","time_start":4.85,"time_end":8.33},{"position":5,"content":"Is it urgent?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-3-2024-08-18-22-20-31/5.mp3","time_start":8.33,"time_end":9.65},{"position":6,"content":"I can try to reach her at the resort.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-3-2024-08-18-22-20-31/6.mp3","time_start":9.65,"time_end":11.79},{"position":7,"content":"No need for that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-3-2024-08-18-22-20-31/7.mp3","time_start":11.79,"time_end":13.25},{"position":8,"content":"I just came by to drop off these documents she asked me to sign.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-3-2024-08-18-22-20-31/8.mp3","time_start":13.25,"time_end":17.37},{"position":9,"content":"Can I leave them with you?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-3-2024-08-18-22-20-31/9.mp3","time_start":17.37,"time_end":18.95},{"position":10,"content":"Sure, no problem!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-3-2024-08-18-22-20-31/10.mp3","time_start":18.95,"time_end":20.74},{"position":11,"content":"I'll let her know you dropped them off and give them to her when she returns.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-3-2024-08-18-22-20-31/11.mp3","time_start":20.74,"time_end":24.45},{"position":12,"content":"Here's a post-it, can you write down what it's about so she knows?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-3-2024-08-18-22-20-31/12.mp3","time_start":24.45,"time_end":28.58},{"position":13,"content":"Sure, I'll do that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-3-2024-08-18-22-20-31/13.mp3","time_start":28.58,"time_end":30.59}]}